    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "- [Voiceover] How often do you shower?", 
            "dur": "1.353", 
            "start": "0.315"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Once?", 
            "dur": "0.857", 
            "start": "1.668"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Twice a day?", 
            "dur": "1.056", 
            "start": "2.525"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Some of you may not even shower at all,", 
            "dur": "1.824", 
            "start": "3.581"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but how often should you actually shower?", 
            "dur": "2.756", 
            "start": "5.405"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "According to dermatologists,", 
            "dur": "1.094", 
            "start": "12.729"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Dr. Joshua Zeichner\nand Dr. Ranella Hirsch,", 
            "dur": "3.02", 
            "start": "13.823"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a lot of the reasons we do it\nis because of societal norms", 
            "dur": "3.027", 
            "start": "16.843"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that it&#39;s really more\nof a cultural phenomenon.", 
            "dur": "2.853", 
            "start": "19.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, frequent showering may actually", 
            "dur": "1.744", 
            "start": "22.723"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "be doing you more harm than good.", 
            "dur": "2.676", 
            "start": "24.467"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Showering too often,\nespecially with hot water,", 
            "dur": "2.318", 
            "start": "28.727"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "actually is bad for your skin.", 
            "dur": "1.912", 
            "start": "31.045"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You wash away the good\nbacteria and dry out your skin,", 
            "dur": "2.644", 
            "start": "32.957"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which puts small cracks that put you", 
            "dur": "2.062", 
            "start": "35.601"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in higher risk of infection.", 
            "dur": "1.994", 
            "start": "37.663"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you have babies or toddlers,", 
            "dur": "1.626", 
            "start": "39.657"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "exposing them to dirt and bacteria", 
            "dur": "1.789", 
            "start": "41.283"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "may actually help their\nskin become less sensitive,", 
            "dur": "2.585", 
            "start": "43.072"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "preventing allergies and\nconditions like eczema.", 
            "dur": "3.228", 
            "start": "45.657"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, back to the question.", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "48.885"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How often should you shower?", 
            "dur": "1.836", 
            "start": "50.485"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In general, you can\nprobably skip a day or two.", 
            "dur": "2.745", 
            "start": "52.321"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Taking one every two to three days,", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "55.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that doesn&#39;t seem so bad, right?", 
            "dur": "2.26", 
            "start": "57.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For those no shower days,", 
            "dur": "1.19", 
            "start": "60.278"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just use a washcloth or\na cleansing towelette", 
            "dur": "2.058", 
            "start": "61.468"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on the grosser parts of your body,", 
            "dur": "1.902", 
            "start": "63.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "under arms, under breasts, genitals,", 
            "dur": "2.18", 
            "start": "65.428"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "your butt, and your face.", 
            "dur": "2.158", 
            "start": "67.608"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Think of all the water you&#39;ll save.", 
            "dur": "1.885", 
            "start": "69.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Mother Earth will be pleased.", 
            "dur": "2.469", 
            "start": "71.651"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Of course, your showering\nneeds will depend on", 
            "dur": "1.908", 
            "start": "74.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "climate and how active you\nare, but be reasonable.", 
            "dur": "3.252", 
            "start": "76.028"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you&#39;re filthy, hit the showers.", 
            "dur": "2.488", 
            "start": "79.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(shower sounds)", 
            "dur": "4.84", 
            "start": "85.89"
        }
    ], 
